| successor    = {{ill|Ichishi no Nagaochi|ja|市磯長尾市|en:draft|6=simple|7=User:Immanuelle/Ichishi no Nagaochi}}
|image=File:Ohyamato-jinja Haiden.jpg|caption=She was the first priestess of [[Ōyamato Shrine]] but was replaced}}{{complex}}
